      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i hear what u say about it being professional, but the timing is just so perfect. it's like they saw me looking into the offshore stuff and instead of shutting me down they just moved me into a glass box where everyone can see what i'm doing all day. i feel like i'm being watched more now than i was before the promotion. don't u think it's a bit too coincidental?",
